Simple secret creation:

  $ init_password_store testpassword
  $ sala set foo/@bar <<EOF
  > testpassword
  > secret
  > secret
  > EOF
  Enter the master passphrase: 
  
  Type a new secret for foo/@bar: 
  Confirm: 
  
  $ decrypt_secret foo/@bar testpassword
  secret (no-eol)

  $ cleanup

