Set a secret, using SALADIR:

  $ mkdir store
  $ (cd store && init_password_store testpassword)
  $ SALADIR=store sala set foo <<EOF
  > testpassword
  > secret
  > secret
  > EOF
  Enter the master passphrase: 
  
  Type a new secret for foo: 
  Confirm: 
  
  $ (cd store && decrypt_secret foo testpassword)
  secret (no-eol)

  $ test -f foo
  [1]

  $ cleanup

